      Creates a GameOver screen and stores the Malice object that created this screen, the music currently playing, the player object from Game Screen, and the class that the player chose.

      MainMenu(Malice g, com.badlogic.gdx.audio.Music m)
      Creates a MainMenu screen and stores the Malice object that created this screen as well as the music object that is currently playing.
      Splash(Malice g)
